(290, 1, '2016-11-12 16:15:51', '2016-11-12 13:15:51', '<h1>Yerlan Battashevitch Sydykov</h1>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-291" src="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/erlan-219x300.jpg" alt="erlan" width="219" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Rector of L.N. Gumilyov Eurasian National University, Kazakhstan</strong>\r\n\r\nOn July 26, 2011 by the order of the President of the Republic of Kazakhstan Yerlan Battashevitch Sydykov was appointed Rector of L.N. Gumilyov Eurasian National University. Prior to this appointment has also worked in the higher education system of the Republic of Kazakhstan. Yerlan Battashevitch has made his career from trainee researcher to the head of the higher education institution. Professor, Doctor of Historical Sciences, Academician of the National Academy of Sciences of the Republic of Kazakhstan.\r\n\r\nY. B. Sydykov is an author of more than 200 scientific and methodological articles, 4 manuals, and 20 monographs.\r\n\r\nSince December 2011 he is the Chairman of the National Congress of historians, in 2016 he was elected a member of Maslikhat of Astana VI convocation, a member of the Council of Relations with Religious Associations under the Government of the Republic of Kazakhstan, member of the Expert Council under the Security Council of the Republic of Kazakhstan, member of the Public Council under the Ministry of Internal Affairs of the Republic of Kazakhstan , member of the Political Council of the Party "Nur Otan". He is the chief editor of the international scientific and popular historical journal «Mangi El», chief editor, project manager of the collection of scientific articles "The people in the flow of history," the chief editor of book series "Gumilyov’s World" and "Issues of Eurasianism", he is a member of the editorial board of the All-Russian scientific journal "Humanitarian sciences in Siberia," a member of the Club of chief editors, Chairman of the Public Council of JSC "NC Astana EXPO-2017".\r\n\r\nSince 2015 he is Vice-President of the Eurasian Association of Universities, the Chairman of the Council of Rectors of higher educational institutions of the Republic of Kazakhstan.\r\n\r\nHe was awarded the badge "Honorary Worker of Education of the Republic of Kazakhstan" (2001), medals "10 years of Independence of the Republic of Kazakhstan" (2001), "10 years of the Constitution of the Republic of Kazakhstan" (2005), was awarded the title of "Kazakhstan''s honourable figure" (2005), was awarded Order "Parasat" (2010), jubilee medals "20 years of Independence of the Republic of Kazakhstan" (2011), "20 years of the Constitution of the Republic of Kazakhstan" (2015), "20 years of the Assembly of people of Kazakhstan" (2015), the Order of the II degree "Barys" (2015) of the IPA CIS medal "For strengthening of parliamentary cooperation" (2015), Appreciation of the President of the Republic of Kazakhstan (2016), diploma of Senate of Kazakhstan (2016).\r\n\r\nHe is married and has three children.', 'Erlan Battashevitch Sydykov', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'erlan', '', '', '2016-11-20 08:08:45', '2016-11-20 05:08:45', '', 0, 'http://ehelf.loc/?page_id=290', 0, 'page', '', 0),
