(353, 1, '2016-11-14 17:11:25', '2016-11-14 14:11:25', '<strong>ACADEMIC QUALITY ENHANCEMENT OFFICE OF THE PROVOST\r\nTranslation of the NU Experience</strong>\r\nMay 26, 2016\r\nNazarbayev University, Block C3, room # 1010\r\nSession: <strong>Quality Enhancement through Annual Program Review</strong>\r\nTarget audience: faculty and administrative staff of HEIs and QA agencies.\r\nThe session will provide a platform for sharing NU’s experience in implementing academic quality enhancement processes, as well as an opportunity to discuss, explore challenges and share good QA/E practices by Kazakhstani higher education institutions.\r\nSession Program:\r\n<table> <tr> <td>\r\n11:45 – 11:55 </td> <td>\r\nSession Opening – Chair Welcome Speech\r\n \r\nChair:  Dr. Duncan Priestley, Head of Academic Quality Enhancement <a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Duncan-Priestleys-Bio_eng.pdf"><strong>link</strong> </a>, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University </td> </tr>\r\n\r\n<tr> <td>\r\n<strong>11:55 – 12:15 </strong></td> <td>\r\n<strong>The Role of Institutional Research in Quality Enhancement Processes</strong>\r\n \r\nPresented by:\r\n1) Dr. Felly Chiteng Kot, Institutional Research Analyst, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University; <a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Felly-Chiteng-Kots-Bio_eng.pdf"><strong>link</strong></a>\r\n2) Ms. Ainur Satekova, Manager, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University. </td> </tr>\r\n \r\n<tr> <td>\r\n<strong>12:15 – 12:35</strong> </td> \r\n </td> <td>\r\n<strong>Annual Monitoring and Review of Educational Delivery</strong>\r\n \r\nPresented by:\r\n1) Ms. Aizhan Mussina, Senior Manager, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University;\r\n2) Ms. Aliya Suleimenova, Manager, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University. </td> </tr>\r\n\r\n<tr> <td>\r\n<strong>12:35 – 13:00</strong> </td> <td> \r\n<strong>Closing Session – Q&A and concluding remarks </strong></td> </tr> </table>\r\n \r\nContact informa