(473, 1, '2016-11-14 20:18:26', '2016-11-14 17:18:26', 'Eurasian Higher Education Leaders’ Forum - 2014\r\n\r\nSuccessful Universities: what are they and how to build one?\r\n\r\n1. Panel session: What is a Successful University?\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Aslan Sarinzhipov, Minister of Education and Science of the Republic of Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nModerator: Alan Ruby, Senior Research Fellow, University of Pennsylvania, USA\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n- William Boulding, Dean, Fuqua School of Business, Duke University, USA\r\n\r\n- Jane Knight, Adjunct Professor, University of Toronto, Canada\r\n\r\n- Amantai Nurmagambetov, Rector, Zhubanov Aktobe Regional State University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Humphrey Tonkin, President Emeritus, University of Hartford, Connecticut, USA\r\n\r\n- Jan Vermunt, Deputy Head, Faculty of Education, University of Cambridge, UK\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n2. Panel session: How to Build a Successful University: new or from existing?\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Les Ebdon, Director of Fair Access to Higher Education, Office for Fair Access, UK\r\n\r\nModerator: Simon Jones, Provost, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n- Mary Canning, Member of the Royal Irish Academy, Ireland\r\n\r\n- Asylbek Kozhakhmetov, Rector, International Business Academy, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Stavros Yiannouka, Senior Advisor, Lee Kuan Yew School of Public Policy, Singapore\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n3. Panel session: Students'' Perspective on Successful University\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Rok Primožič, Chairperson, European Students’ Union, Belgium\r\n\r\nModerator: Timothy Reagan, Dean, Graduate School of Education, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n- Guldana Akhmetova, PhD student, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Askhat Oralov, Master''s student, L.N. Gumilyov Eurasian National University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Kamila Rollan, Undergraduate student, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Liz Winter, University Lecturer, Cambridge University, UK\r\n\r\n- Angela Yiu, Vice President for Academic Exchange, Sophia University, Japan\r\n\r\n- Bakyt Zlobin, Master''s student, Serikbayev East Kazakhstan State Technical University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n4. Panel session: Faculty''s Perspective on Successful University\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Fatima Zhakypova, National Educational Expert, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nModerator: Loretta O''Donnell, Vice-Provost for Academic Affairs, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n- Matthew Hartley, Chair, Higher Education Division, Professor, University of Pennsylvania, USA\r\n\r\n- Kanybek Isakov, Rector, Osh State University, Kyrgyz Republic\r\n\r\n- Beibit Mamrayev, Rector, Dosmukhamedov Atyrau State University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Rustem Omarov, Chair, Biotechnology and Microbiology Department, Gumilyov Eurasian National University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Aida Sagintayeva, Chief Executive Director, Graduate School of Education, Nazarbayev University, Kazakshtan\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n5. Panel session: Successful Research Universities\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Simon Jones, Provost, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nModerator: Dennis de Tray, Advisor to President, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n- Zhexenbek Adilov, Rector, Satpayev Kazakh National Technical University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n- Jennifer Francis, Senior Associate Dean for Programs, Fuqua School of Business, Duke University, USA\r\n\r\n- Zhumakhan Myrkhalykov, Rector, Auezov South Kazakhstan State University, Kazakhstan', 'Speakers 2014', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'speakers-2014', '', '', '2016-11-14 20:18:26', '2016-11-14 17:18:26', '', 0, 'http://ehelf.loc/?page_id=473', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(474, 1, '2016-11-14 20:14:35', '2016-11-14 17:14:35', '<strong>Eurasian Higher Education Leaders’ Forum – 2015\r\n\r\nGraduate Employability in the 21st Century\r\n\r\nOverview session</strong><strong>\r\n\r\nOpenning speech: Aslan Sarinzhipov, Minister of Education and Science of the Republic of Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nModerator: Rakhman Alshanov, President of the Association of Higher Educational Institutions of the Republic of Kazakhstan, Rector, "Turan" University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Hugh Lauder, Professor of Education and Political Economy, University of Bath, UK\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n-	Berik Kamaliyev, Vice-President,  JSC, National Company “Kazakhstan Temir Zholy” (“Kazakhstan Railways”), Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n-	Erezhep Mambetkaziyev, President, Kazakh-American Free University, Kazakhstan  \r\n\r\n-	Timothy Miller, General Director, Tengizchevroil, Kazakhstan\r\n<hr>\r\n1. Panel session: Global Skills\r\n\r\nModerator: Simon Jones, Provost, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Jamil Salmi, A Global Tertiary Education Expert, Morocco\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n-	Seeram Ramakrishna, Director, Center for Nanofibers & Nanotechnology, National University of Singapore, Singapore\r\n\r\n-	Jamilya Nurmanbetova, First Vice-Rector, Gumilyov Eurasian National University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n-	Duncan van Bergen,Vice President and Country Chair, Shell, Kazakhstan\r\n<hr>\r\n2. Panel session: Perceptions of Employability, Skills and Individual Aspiration in a Diversifying Economy\r\n\r\nModerator: Alan Ruby, Senior Research Fellow, University of Pennsylvania Graduate School of Education, USA\r\n\r\nKeynote speaker: Alper Akdeniz, Managing Partner for Eurasia, PricewaterhouseCoopers (PwC), Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nPanelists:\r\n\r\n-	Arstan Gazaliyev, Rector, Karaganda State Technical University, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n-	Kanysh Tuleushin, Member of Managing Board, Managing Director, Baiterek National Holding, Kazakhstan\r\n\r\n-	Stavros Yiannouka, Chief Execu