(818, 1, '2016-11-18 02:25:14', '2016-11-17 23:25:14', '<strong>PROGRAM</strong>\r\n\r\nOffice of the Registrar seminar\r\n<a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Aktymbaeva.pdf"><strong>Aigul Aktymbaeva</strong></a>, Director, Department of Continuing Education, Graduate School of Education\r\n\r\n<a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Rebecca-Carter.pdf"><strong>Rebecca Carter</strong></a>, Registrar, Office of the Registrar\r\n\r\n<a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Meruyert-Akhmadiyeva.pdf"><strong>Meruert Akhmandiyeva</strong></a>, General Manager, Office of the Registrar\r\n\r\n<a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Saltanat-Beisembina.pdf"><strong>Saltanat Beisenbina </strong></a>, Manager, Office of the Registrar\r\n\r\n<a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Tuyakbaev.pdf"><strong>Olzhas Tuyakbayev</strong></a> , Consultant, Office of the Registrar\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Venue</strong></td>\r\n<td>Nazarbayev University</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Date and Time:</strong></td>\r\n<td>May 26, 2016 09:00 – 17:30</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Objectives:</strong></td>\r\n<td>To discuss best world practices that can be used in Kazakhstani realities, current trends and ways to optimize work in the Office of the Registrar.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>May 26, 2016</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong> 08:30 – 09:00</strong></td>\r\n<td>Registration</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>09:00 – 11:00 </strong></td>\r\n<td>General Forum session</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>11:00 – 11:45</strong></td>\r\n<td>Coffee break</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>12:00 – 12:10</strong></td>\r\n<td>Introduction: introducing participants, presenting objectives and future plans</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>12:10 - 13:00</strong></td>\r\n<td>Session 1:\r\n· OR Global model\r\n· Partners’ experience\r\n· Best world practices\r\n· OR career deve