(900, 1, '2016-11-20 08:07:55', '2016-11-20 05:07:55', '<strong>Sharing NU Experience</strong>\r\n\r\nMay 26, 2016\r\n\r\nSeminar: Conducting research in Education (Social Sciences)\r\n\r\n<strong>Audience:</strong> faculty, representatives from research institutes, administrative staff of universities responsible for the implementation of the research, representatives from the Ministry of Education and Science of the Republic of Kazakhstan\r\n\r\nThis session is a platform for discussion of the issues related to conducting research in the humanities\r\n\r\n<strong>Topics for discussion:</strong>\r\n\r\n✓ Conducting research;\r\n✓ Research ethics;\r\n✓ Publishing academic papers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Important information:</strong>\r\n\r\nIn order to create a fruitful and useful discussion of the issues related to the conducting research in the humanities we are kindly asking those, who are interested in attending the seminar, to email us a list of questions to be raised at the session relevant to the proposed topics of discussion <strong>until May 15, 2016 </strong> at dina.gungor@nu.edu.kz\r\n<strong>\r\nSpeakers: </strong>\r\nDuishon Shamatov, Associate Professor, Graduate School of Education\r\nAli Ait Si Mhamed, Associate Professor, Graduate School of Education\r\nKairat Kurakbayev, Director, Research Institute, Graduate School of Education\r\n\r\n<strong>Contact:</strong>\r\n+7 (7172) 70 66 30, Zakir Jumakulov, zakir.jumakulov@nu.edu.kz\r\n+7 (7172) 70 64 38, Dina Gungor, dina.gungor@nu.edu.kz\r\n\r\n<strong>Program\r\nSeminar: «Conducting research in the humanities»</strong>\r\n\r\nDate: May 26, 2016\r\nVenue: Nazarbayev University, Block ___, Room ____\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>14:30 – 14:40</td>\r\n<td>Registration</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>14:40 – 14:50</td>\r\n<td>Opening session</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>14:50 – 15:10</td>\r\n<td>Conducting research in Education (Social Sciences)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>15:10 – 15:25</td>\r\