(901, 1, '2016-11-20 08:08:06', '2016-11-20 05:08:06', '<strong>ACADEMIC QUALITY ENHANCEMENT OFFICE OF THE PROVOST\r\nTranslation of the NU Experience</strong>\r\nMay 26, 2016\r\nNazarbayev University, Block C3, room # 1010\r\nSession: <strong>Quality Enhancement through Annual Program Review</strong>\r\nTarget audience: faculty and administrative staff of HEIs and QA agencies.\r\nThe session will provide a platform for sharing NU’s experience in implementing academic quality enhancement processes, as well as an opportunity to discuss, explore challenges and share good QA/E practices by Kazakhstani higher education institutions.\r\nSession Program:\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>11:45 – 11:55</td>\r\n<td>Session Opening – Chair Welcome SpeechChair: Dr. Duncan Priestley, Head of Academic Quality Enhancement <a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Duncan-Priestleys-Bio_eng.pdf"><strong>link</strong> </a>, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>11:55 – 12:15 </strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>The Role of Institutional Research in Quality Enhancement Processes</strong>Presented by:\r\n1) Dr. Felly Chiteng Kot, Institutional Research Analyst, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University; <a href="http://ehelf.loc/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Felly-Chiteng-Kots-Bio_eng.pdf"><strong>link</strong></a>\r\n2) Ms. Ainur Satekova, Manager, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>12:15 – 12:35</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Annual Monitoring and Review of Educational Delivery</strong>Presented by:\r\n1) Ms. Aizhan Mussina, Senior Manager, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University;\r\n2) Ms. Aliya Suleimenova, Manager, Office of the Provost, Nazarbayev University.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>12:35 – 13:00</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Closing Session – Q&amp;A and concluding remarks </strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nContact information:\r\nacademicquality@nu